components.stack

Interface Stack<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, StackKernel<T>, Standard<Stack<T>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Stack1L, StackSecondary, StackSL

    public interface Stack<T>
extends StackKernel<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Additional functionality upon the bare-bones functionality afforded by the StackKernel interface. All method implementations must, by design, use only the StackKernel methods to perform operations on the component.
    Author:
    Matthew Shoemaker
